**-^** (\*)
    Print a short message about the syntax of the command, then exits.
**-?** (\*)
    Print a full usage (help) message, including the explanation of
    options, then exits.
**-**\ **-version** (\*)
    Print GMT version and exit.
**-**\ **-show-sharedir** (\*)
    Print full path to GMT share directory and exit.
